==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reabsorb
<hw>Re`ab*sorb"</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧`⟦acr⟧b*s⟦ocir⟧rb")</pr>, <pos>v.
t.</pos> <def>To absorb again; to draw in, or imbibe, again what has
been effused, extravasated, or thrown off; to swallow up again; <as>as,
to <ex>reabsorb</ex> chyle, lymph, etc.</as>; -- used esp. of
fluids.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reabsorption</ent>⟦br⟧
